column5: For those that were looking for storage,and can get up this way,I got a sweet deal. Winterize,both motor(inboard) and bottom end,also, add a shrink wrap and the kicker,storage.Did I mention,flushed in the spring and ready to go. 845 taxes in. Where,,,,,,,Blue moon marine.  I have done some calling(well except for the irishfield storage yard)LOL And this by far was the best deal out there,and close to home.  Oh BTW,she,ll be up for sale come May.
